GG_FREEZE_CSS - Gun Game

This map based on a free 4 play game (War INC. Battlezone). It was originally for Deathmatch that game and based on FY_ICEWORLD but its now for Arms Race and looks like a giant fridge :)

It is a small and realy fast map. I hope u like it. 

Map Covered by GodWan4

Check out the [Counter-Strike](http://gamebanana.com/cs/maps/168499 "GG_FREEZE_CS") and [Counter-Strike: Global Offensive](http://gamebanana.com/csgo/maps/167938 "AR_FREEZE_CSGO") versions too.
